# **NEW!** The Carnival has arrived in DigiGods, and it's not your average funfair. The Carnival Update transforms the virtual realms of DigiGods into a dazzling, chaotic playground of flips, trails, ragdoll madness, potions, and more!

**CREATE, PLAY, & SHARE** in a physics-based sandbox environment where you can shoot, parkour, or simulate any type of gameplay you desire, harnessing the very best of VR.
